  "1706800": {
    "name": "The Art Of Flight",
    "steam_appid": 1706800,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/eec8f7f7b3cb4866dd575d196a70eb8e.poster.avif?t=1760565353\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/eec8f7f7b3cb4866dd575d196a70eb8e.webm?t=1760565353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/eec8f7f7b3cb4866dd575d196a70eb8e.mp4?t=1760565353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《飞行奇艺》是对八九十年代动作街机游戏的致敬，并对该类型游戏进行了全新的创新。它不再有传统的生命计数器，而是可以同时操纵多艘飞船，击落一波又一波的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于每次游戏都是随机的，并且有超过 60 个关卡可玩，因此每次游戏的感觉都不相同。你可以将注意力从一艘飞船转移到另一艘，体验一场充满牺牲、战友情谊和冒险的史诗太空战斗。但不要放松警惕……如果你所有的飞船都被摧毁，游戏就结束了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/c7e8ac2049c78d8b552f4dd2ed98becf.poster.avif?t=1760565353\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/c7e8ac2049c78d8b552f4dd2ed98becf.webm?t=1760565353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/c7e8ac2049c78d8b552f4dd2ed98becf.mp4?t=1760565353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乐趣并不仅仅局限于单人游戏……你可以在本地合作中与多达 4 位好友一起游玩。在飞行过程中，如果一名玩家失去了所有飞船，朋友们可以帮助救回飞船，让游戏的乐趣更长久。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供多种模式供探索，可以反复尝试，让你实现完美主义的心愿。在一波波无尽的敌人中，争夺高分、解救被俘虏的船只，壮大自己的舰队，迎接不断增强的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/844f0579a476599ab1fc3c3c02a39762.poster.avif?t=1760565353\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/844f0579a476599ab1fc3c3c02a39762.webm?t=1760565353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/844f0579a476599ab1fc3c3c02a39762.mp4?t=1760565353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每段情节的顺序都是随机的，以创造独特的挑战，迫使你改变游戏方式。在游戏中不断前进，解锁更多的道具和情节。飞越小行星带，沿着滑流滑行，获取道具，并使用你的飞船以独特的方式击败敌人头目。动态的背景音乐会伴随着你行动，根据你的动作做出响应。因此你可使用单舰能力，让你麾下除一艘飞船之外的所有飞船时间停止，指挥你的中队绕过敌人和紧追不放的导弹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/3199aecd7d84a6946da9d715d215407b.poster.avif?t=1760565353\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/3199aecd7d84a6946da9d715d215407b.webm?t=1760565353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706800/extras/3199aecd7d84a6946da9d715d215407b.mp4?t=1760565353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏都会带给你独特的感觉，而且关卡的顺序会在游戏过程中随机变化……60 多个关卡等着你去体验，不断游玩，一睹全部关卡的风采！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多达 4 名玩家可同时加入游戏。所有模式均可进行本地合作！还提供本地对战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam 排行榜，让你展现你的好胜之心。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >得分机制，让你在游戏中迎险而上。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种各样的道具和头目关卡，不断给你新鲜感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据你的行动创造的动态配乐。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁模式和情节，便于重玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以调节速度，让你以轻松的节奏享受行动的乐趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持控制器：请使用控制器享受最佳游戏体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 德语<strong>*</strong>, 日语<strong>*</strong>, 韩语<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<strong>*</strong>, 俄语<strong>*</strong>, 简体中文<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
